{"tid":1128272,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤個youtube channel會唔會一鋪清袋?","createTime":"2019-04-27T17:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T18:40:26.000Z","uid":67294,"like":38,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d22ae701b5e3a43eb6a18461352c2435421f5f98","tid":1128272,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"遲出糧未搞清事實就恰鳩人係18線model仔開post公審人<br />\n<br />\n個程美段雖然比唔上貝依霖, 但話哂都著件車厘龜衫叫左幫你做到個gimmick吸引多左人睇<br />\n依家你公審人又公開哂佢show錢, 仲叫人唔好用佢想斷人米路, 係咪做到咁絕?<br />\n老實講, 你個台做得起咪又係靠賣肉, 真係想睇late night show睇煮野食我都唔洗睇你啦<br />\n<br />\n不過我相信以你知名度, 實仲有一大班18線model仔肯上你台比你公然性騷擾博上位<br />\n但經過今次呢件事, 至少我一定唔會再比views你<br />\n你都係食返之前條水得閒抽下政治水吸黃絲觀眾算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f88b760590b210c1dc6e0d900441ec4c4b2da1d","tid":1128272,"uid":29080,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:18:02.000Z","msg":"開頭睇過下<br />\n之後頂唔順佢乜都要講句粗口落去又唔好笑就冇睇了<br />\n呀杜生，唔係咩都加句粗口就等於好笑架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd409209478ed9a0766f12d70cf7d5ec60db837a","tid":1128272,"uid":22694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"事實係content開始悶<br />\n又開唔到新節目<br />\n<br />\n利申:有睇肥強減肥"},{"pid":"b5a332d19d40103fc1ad8595009e8e4933e8bb1e","tid":1128272,"uid":25019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"睇班女渣 睇你煮埋d濕鳩餸咩 冇廚藝可言<br />\n仲要覺得自己係大老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0804af3118496a6ebaeabeabe5e197eec273d3","tid":1128272,"uid":35678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"睇過幾次,次次都屌個鑊,唔岩用未換囉,睇到我R晒頭"},{"pid":"79f9ff73ed461e341713c26644b49c64a9c0fd0f","tid":1128272,"uid":48369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04